<a href="http://www.freshplaza.com/news_detail.asp?id=99862 #SlideFrame_1" target="_self">http://www.freshplaza.com/news_detail.asp?id=99862#SlideFrame_1</a></p><p><i>ABC.net.au</i>, ‘National Party wade into ginger row’, 11 September 2012</p><p>
<a href="http://www.freshplaza.com/news_detail.asp?id=100588#SlideFrame_1" target="_self">http://www.freshplaza.com/news_detail.asp?id=100588#SlideFrame_1</a></p><p>AAP, ‘Ginger growers worried by Fiji imports’, 10 September 2012</p><p>
